# PalJS Admin UI

The [admin](mdc:packages/admin) package provides a UI framework for building admin interfaces for Prisma-based applications.

## Key Features
- Built with React and TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS for styling ([tailwind.config.js](mdc:packages/admin/tailwind.config.js))
- Component library for common admin interfaces

## Configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:packages/admin/tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [babel.config.js](mdc:packages/admin/babel.config.js) - Babel configuration for transpilation
- [postcss.config.js](mdc:packages/admin/postcss.config.js) - PostCSS configuration

## Usage
The Admin UI can be integrated into your Prisma-based applications to provide:
- Data browsing and management interfaces
- CRUD operations on Prisma models
- Custom views and forms

Refer to the [README.md](mdc:packages/admin/README.md) for detailed usage instructions.
